This was my first ever project created for computer programming course. It was written in C and required user to input a list of words they want to learn. It would then show a word in one language in a user and ask to translate it. If the translation was right user could go to the next word.
!notice! internal path in code is needed to be  changed according to the path of your choice. Unfortunatelly i wasn't skilled enough back then to make it work seamlessly.
"Ffile" file is a placeholder file with starter words. You can try plugging it in to see how the program works.  
